                <h1>Understanding NCSI: A Global Cybersecurity Benchmark</h1>
                <p>NCSI, or National Cybersecurity Index, is a global metric that evaluates countries' cybersecurity capabilities and resilience. It serves as a benchmarking tool to assess the preparedness and response strategies of nations against cyber threats. By analyzing various aspects, NCSI helps improve cybersecurity policies and fosters international cooperation.</p>
